ng of the people and businesses of our country.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 27.6pt; padding-left:8.4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Nuffield Health is the </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">largest healthcare charity in the UK. In 2012, we helped 800,000 people with th</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">eir healthcare needs. A</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">nnual turnover is £645 million, with approximately 11,000 staff across 300+ sites: </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">31 hospitals, 65 fitness &amp; wellbeing </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">centres</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">, 200 employee wellbeing facilities and 20 medical clinics.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 27.6pt; padding-left:8.4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">We have made employee health and wellbeing key</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt"> aspects of corporate social responsibility, as the country’s largest provider of employee wellbeing services working with more than 1,600 employers to support their staff. There are 100,000+ members in our corporate fitness facilities, with 50,000+ employ</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">ee health screenings provided to them annually.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 27.6pt; padding-left:8.4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">We are the largest provider of physiotherapy services in the UK, continuously investing in our network of over 2,000 experienced, registered physiotherapists to empower recovery and rehabilitation.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 27.6pt; padding-left:8.4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="fon