ze:10pt">Health’s remuneration committee takes independent, external advice that benchmarks executive pay against a selection of leading charities, private and public healthcare </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">organisations</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">, and comparable UK companies. Total compensation is set at 75% of the mar</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">ket median. In the interests of transparency the remuneration for all senior executives is disclosed in our Annual Report and Accounts.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 27.6pt; padding-left:8.4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Nuffield Health has been led by David </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Mobbs</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">, Group Chief Executive, since 2003.</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt"><br style="page-break-before:always; clear:both" /><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Public benefit delivered</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 18pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Arial Narrow'; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal">1.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">Our charitabl</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">e purpose defines our business. All of our services, treatments and facilities, and the funding that enables them, is dedicated to augmenting the nation’s health and wellbeing. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 18pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font-family:'Arial Narrow'; font-size:10pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal">2.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0